{"tid":514075,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上環海味店「影后」 偷完海參仲傾吓計","createTime":"2017-12-30T07:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T07:52:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6fae725b5c269e107697c1dc0e4f2ab3889015","tid":514075,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:50:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171230/20260110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F20260110&d=tq1kDz1fn1a4gO7PTbgixJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=f3eb6f46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F20260110&h=f0b00362\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171230/20260110</a><br />\n<br />\n上環海味店「影后」<br />\n偷完海參仲傾吓計<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】上環永樂街一間海味店，姓陳(34歲)負責人前日發現放在門外貨架的一包海參不翼而飛，昨晨翻看閉路電視，拍攝到是一名女顧客所為，損失的海參值1,180元，陳於昨晨10時左右報警。<br />\n<br />\n從閉路電視畫面所見，該名女子年約50歲，穿紅色衫蓄長髮。前日下午4時半左右，店員正招呼兩名男顧客之際，她將該包海參放入手袋內，得手後也沒有即時離去，反而走入店內，查詢其他貨品的價格，逗留近10分鐘才走，沒有購物。<br />\n<br />\n負責人稱，海味店開業4年，不時發生盜竊案，即今年也拉過兩名竊賊；只是貨品價值不算高，都是放在門外吸引顧客，沒有特別的防盜措施。"},{"pid":"d9ee9e64225503da22bff09acafccac326bf4cb2","tid":514075,"uid":142029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:52:38.000Z","msg":"我第一時間諗起夜神月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}